---

<section class="section" id="about">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="kicker reveal"><span class="num">01</span><span class="lbl">About</span><span class="rule"></span></div>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-copy">
        <p class="big reveal">Hi — I'm Sönke, a software developer from Lübeck. I like the small details — in a cup of coffee, on a bike, or through a viewfinder.</p>
        <p class="reveal d1">Most mornings start with a pour-over and a few tasting notes. Most weekends involve a steel road bike and as much open road as I can find.</p>
        <p class="reveal d2">And somewhere in between there's always a camera within reach, for the small, fast-moving moments I'm forever trying to hold onto.</p>
        <div class="focus-list reveal d2">
          <div class="t">A few favourite things</div>
          <div class="focus-tags">
            <span>Specialty coffee</span><span>Road cycling</span><span>Photography</span><span>Lübeck</span><span>Software</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-cards">
        <div class="icard reveal d1" style="--accent: var(--pink);">
          <div class="k">Home</div>
          <div class="v">Lübeck</div>
          <div class="s">on the German Baltic coast</div>
        </div>
        <div class="icard reveal d2" style="--accent: var(--cyan);">
          <div class="k">Most days</div>
          <div class="v">Writing software</div>
          <div class="s">with a pour-over nearby</div>
        </div>
        <div class="icard reveal d3" style="--accent: var(--purple);">
          <div class="k">Most weekends</div>
          <div class="v">Out on the road bike</div>
          <div class="s">steel frame, long roads</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
